### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders

### Create New Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customer_id": "12345ER",
  "items": [
    {
      "product_id": "P123",
      "quantity": 10,
      "price": 50.00
    },
    {
      "product_id": "P456",
      "quantity": 3,
      "price": 100.00
    },
    {
      "product_id": "P789",
      "quantity": 8,
      "price": 25.00
    }
  ]
}

